imdb.plot outline: Starving Actor Problems is a webisode starring and created by Mallory Low, an actress who's been in the business for over 17 years. It takes a look inside her quirky mind as she comedically humanizes one the most competitive businesses in the world. SAP hopes to connect actors and actresses, whether they be starving or not, in a overly competitive industry, and to bring to light that we all share the same fears, issues, experiences, and awkward moments.
